Implementation Patterns

Direct Implementation
(Standard Onboarding)
Document Capture → OCR Extraction → Data Validation

Biometric Verification
(Identity Confirmation)
Face Capture → Liveness Detection → ID Matching

Compliance Integration
(Regulatory Checks)
Customer Data → AML Screening → Risk Assessment


Technical Implementation Mapping

Current Process			Digital Solution			Implementation Approach
Physical Document Collection	Mobile Document Capture			OCR with quality validation
Manual Data Entry		Automated Data Extraction		AI-powered form filling
In-Person Verification		Biometric Authentication		Face recognition with liveness
